nodes.text: The Wartaki Sea was an open body of shallow water located on Kashyyyk, a planet of the Mytaranor sector. The Wawaatt Archipelago was located in the Wartaki Sea. During the Clone Wars, the Confederacy of Independent Systems conquerred Kachirho, a city of the Wawaatt Archipelago. In order to retake the city, the enemy Galactic Republic brought its landing force to Kachirho by sea.
